{"tid":2512542,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【荷甲韋根】點睇荷甲安曼準備奇蹟護級成功？","createTime":"2021-05-01T19:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T21:06:02.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf13cd52451deb507f46b58ffef4707de9d0954","tid":2512542,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T19:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNPY6nUqQ9ux8dG65HvTRuU8T6TQaHGhKoSGoju2qwCLY?filename=7SALqJu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7SALqJu.jpg&h=eef6896f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左同大家討論 我特別上左荷蘭版既wiki搵呢個表出黎同大家開心share<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講返正題先<br />\n安曼由第八輪已經跌左落降班區<br />\n第十輪起更加坐喺榜尾<br />\n開季超過廿輪都無贏過 直至2月21號先至首勝<br />\n亦由果場開始<br />\n佢地豪取5勝3和不敗戰績<br />\n積分慢慢由單位數慢慢爬升上黎<br />\n去到30場24分擺脫直接降班區位置<br />\n只係落後尾四既威廉二世一分<br />\n隨時連升降班附加賽都唔駛踢<br />\n不過聽晚佢地要對阿積士<br />\n希望會有奇蹟搶到一分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家都支持安曼護級成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f4da8490137c36377a59cdd377789da06d8810","tid":2512542,"uid":54344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:03:15.000Z","msg":"唉比屈dee一燈 呢鋪molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cross.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dda84016cb8eb21f63f7d05b7cf4754510b188f","tid":2512542,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:12:25.000Z","msg":"明明英文版wiki都有呢個表<br />\n懶係野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇馬里迪莫兩個伊朗關鍵球員 近8場拎15分 <br />\n幫球隊由18位升上12位"},{"pid":"e5b883be186e540e3d85729616b9dddbf19396ab","tid":2512542,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8dda84016cb8eb21f63f7d05b7cf4754510b188f","tid":2512542,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20